{
  "stem": "33.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And when I told him where I'm going, he said, no, you cannot go there right now.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But don't worry about it, because you will see your mother later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Men and women were separated, so I was separated from my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I found myself in a column of about five or six women, in a row, of about five or six women.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we were just told to walk ahead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "At the end of these rope was the SS officer, who didn't look old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I suppose when you're 18, not old is probably under 30.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He was perfectly attired, and I suppose that was very visible to us in contrast to our miserable appearance after a three-day journey.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "His uniform was just perfectly pressed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "His boots were shining.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He had a riding crop, a whip, in his hand.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And he was whistling a tune all the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "He never uttered a word, but with the movement of his wrist, with his riding crop, he was pointing to the left or to the right to where each of us should go.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Again, we did not know the identity of this monster at that time, but this was Dr.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Josef Mengele, chief medical officer of Auschwitz, responsible for the death of hundreds of thousands of people, and also the experiments that he used, using human beings as guinea pigs.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I was with my next-door neighbor in the same row, I remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And she had her very old mother with her that she was sort of holding by her arm.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I remember them being sent to the left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I sort of took a step in that direction, because I wanted to go with somebody I knew, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But he did point me to the right.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
